    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1 class="main-title">Happy Birthday Sonam!</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">A special day for a special person 💕</p>
        </div>

        <div class="birthday-card">
            <div class="cake-icon">🎂✨</div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <div class="message-line">Happy Birthday, <span class="highlight">gorgeous!</span> 🎉</div>
                <div class="message-line">Hope your day's as <span class="highlight">beautiful, fun, and unforgettable</span> as your smile.</div>
                <div class="message-line">If I had one wish, it'd be to make you <span class="highlight">laugh till your cheeks hurt</span>… and maybe steal that smile 😉</div>
                <div class="message-line">Here's to your day — and maybe some <span class="highlight">unforgettable memories together?</span> 💫❤️</div>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <button class="celebration-btn" onclick="celebrate()">🎉 Celebrate! 🎉</button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Wishing you all the love, laughter, and cake your heart desires! 🍰💕</p>
        </div>
